      "factId": "hz.web.358d75f5e1165f0d.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "The settlement agreement requires Crossroads to pay $1.64 million.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Our settlement with Crossroads underscores the need to hold companies accountable for fraudulent practices.",
