      "factId": "hz.web.358d75f5e1165f0d.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "When powerful companies use their power to cheat our government, California taxpayers are also cheated,” &lt;b&gt;said Attorney General Bonta&lt;/b&gt;.",
