; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;b&gt;OAKLAND &lt;/b&gt;— California Attorney General Rob Bonta today announced a &lt;a href=&quot;https://oag.ca.gov/system/files/attachments/press-docs/2026.03.27%20Crossroads%20Settlement%20Agreement%20Fully%20Executed.pdf&quot;&gt;settlement&lt;/a&gt; with commercial fleet lender Crossroads Equipment Lease and Finance (Crossroads) over alleged false claims for reimbursements under the California Capital Access Program (CalCAP).",
